1. Moram da uradim *čišćenje* sobe pre nego što dođu gosti. (I have to do *cleaning* the room before the guests arrive.)
2. *Čišćenje* je bilo veoma naporno zbog velike količine prljavštine. (*Cleaning* was very tiring because of the large amount of dirt.)
3. Radnici *čišćenja* su došli da očiste park nakon koncerta. (The *cleaning* workers came to clean the park after the concert.)
4. Kada bismo više vremena posvetili *čišćenju*, kuća bi nam uvek bila čista. (If we devoted more time to *cleaning*, our house would always be clean.)
5. Ovaj proizvod je namenjen za *čišćenje* kamenca u kupatilu. (This product is intended for *cleaning* limescale in the bathroom.)
6. Pored redovnog *čišćenja*, potrebno je obaviti i detaljno *čišćenje* svake godine. (In addition to regular *cleaning*, it is necessary to perform a detailed *cleaning* every year.)
7. Ovaj uređaj olakšava *čišćenje* podova jer ima integrisanu usisivač. (This device makes *cleaning* floors easier because it has an integrated vacuum cleaner.)
8. *Čišćenje* teških mašina zahteva posebnu opremu i veštine. (*Cleaning* heavy machinery requires special equipment and skills.)
9. Vlasnik hotela angažovao je agenciju za *čišćenje* da održava higijenu u sobama. (The hotel owner hired a *cleaning* agency to maintain hygiene in the rooms.)
10. *Čišćenje* okoline i očuvanje prirode su ključni za održivost planete. (*Cleaning* the environment and preserving nature are crucial for the sustainability of the planet.)